    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "That's so cool @JanPetr. Should we bundle every single analytics service in its own widget to avoid writing again and again the same code?\r\n\r\nLike:\r\n\r\n```\r\nsearch.addWidget(instantsearch.widgets.analytics.googleAnalytics());\r\nsearch.addWidget(instantsearch.widgets.analytics.segment());\r\nsearch.addWidget(instantsearch.widgets.analytics.kissmetrics());\r\nsearch.addWidget(instantsearch.widgets.analytics({\r\n    pushFunction: function(formattedParameters, state, results) {\r\n      // any other analytics service\r\n    }\r\n  });\r\n```\r\n",
