    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Thanks @redox.\r\nThat's what we decided to omit (https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/pull/1616#issuecomment-263539378). It'd require maintaining those services APIs in instantsearch.js and would become pain in future.\r\nBecause of that we settled on exposing only `pushFunction` which the widget will run in the right time with right data.\r\n\r\nWe will publish a guide how to integrate few services (like [currently commented out in app.js](https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/pull/1626/files#diff-1765d0005076c116a75098c1162e835bR34)).\r\n\r\nBut I don't understand what you mean by\r\n> to avoid writing again and again the same code?\r\n\r\nI don't see issue with repeating code.",
